article.description: — Elijah McCadden had 13 points as Georgia Southern topped South Florida 53-41 on Saturday.
article.headline: McCadden lifts Georgia Southern past South Florida 53-41
article.linkText: McCadden lifts Georgia Southern past South Florida 53-41
article.story: TAMPA, Fla. -- — Elijah McCadden had 13 points as Georgia Southern topped South Florida 53-41 on Saturday. Cam Bryant had 11 points for Georgia Southern (2-0). Andrei Savrasov added 10 points. Kamari Brown had seven rebounds. DJ Patrick had 18 points for the Bulls (1-1). Russel Tchewa added nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25------ Information from: Automated Insights, http://automatedinsights.com/ ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
